Class ProfileEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.onarandombox.multiverseinventories.share.ProfileEntry
  • public final class ProfileEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    Indicates how a Sharable should be stored in the profile file. Serves as a lookup for finding a sharable based on it's file tag.

      • lookup

        public static Sharable lookup​(boolean stat,
                              java.lang.String fileTag)
        Used to look up a Sharable by it's file tag.
        Parameters:
        stat - True means this sharable is in the stats section of the player file.
        fileTag - The string representing where the sharable is stored in the player file.
